  <brief_title>Isoflavones and the Coronary Circulation in Men and Women With Coronary Artery Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Genistein (Supro®) on Coronary Artery Diameter and Blood Flow in Men and Women With Coronary Heart Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
