  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the effect of genistein administration on coronary
      arteries in humans. We will measure the size of a coronary artery and the speed and amount of
      blood flow in response after subjects have ingested Supro® drinks (a soy protein drink
      containing genistein).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
